<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13063931/switzerland_graubuenden-ski-region_st-moritz_family-mountain-view.jpg" alt="familyski" data-udi="umb://media/aa5e2f0e0d3047898bdf8088970aa029" /></p>
<p><strong>Family fun in Feb</strong> - Skiing in February is the perfect time of year - the ice cold days of winter has passed and then sun has started to shine higher in the sky but there is still plenty of snowfall to be had. It is also the perfect time to go on a family skiing holiday, as half-term falls within this month.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c}" class="c-btn">View ski deals</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Best ski resorts in February</h2>
<p>A selection of some of our favourite resorts to visit in February: </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/799f63184c52477c94171a057c16e540" href="/{localLink:umb://document/799f63184c52477c94171a057c16e540}" title="Avoriaz">Avoriaz, France</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13070619/inghams-best-family-ski-resorts-avoriaz.jpg" alt="avoriazfrance" data-udi="umb://media/e1d8594b9ccb40f286d6d56681377958" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Great for <a data-udi="umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875}" title="Family Ski Holidays">families </a></li>
<li>Small, family friendly, purpose built ski resort</li>
<li>Excellent quality lessons with ESF ski school<br /><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></li>
<li>Perfect for learning</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/f5a15898b6694ef6a1c755346a0e1ba8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f5a15898b6694ef6a1c755346a0e1ba8}" title="Corvara &amp; Colfosco">Corvara, Italy</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13055596/finland_lapland_levi_snow-shoe-walking.jpg" alt="leviresort" data-udi="umb://media/6fb9553241024ada8a25134f06063030" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Great for couples </li>
<li>Fantastic local cuisine and drinks</li>
<li>Delight village nestled in the Dolomites</li>
<li>Easy access to multiple ski areas</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50}" title="Saas Fee">Saas Fee, Switzerland</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13066986/snowsheing-off-piste-above-saas-fee.jpg" alt="saasfeeresort" data-udi="umb://media/f6bff9f5432049febe11cf51c040b9e3" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Great for <a data-udi="umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb}" title="Group Ski Holidays">groups</a></li>
<li>Ideal for a short getaway with friends</li>
<li>A lot of variety with all levels of runs, off-piste and snow-parks</li>
<li>Perfect for skiers and snowboarders</li>
<li>Lots of restaurants and bars</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/5c5a68def0234451a0e7113b85bac993" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5c5a68def0234451a0e7113b85bac993}" title="Hochgurgl"><span>Hochgurgl, Austria</span></a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13050947/austria_hochgurgl_sporthotel_-olymp_view-of-hotel-exterior.jpg" alt="hochgurglaustria" data-udi="umb://media/f9b78092fe4c41c6882b2a3c9c9893ff" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Great for <a data-udi="umb://document/43b759307a674eaba22751fc5ef9501a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/43b759307a674eaba22751fc5ef9501a}" title="Single Ski Holidays">solo</a> skiers</li>
<li>Connected to other ski areas for lots of exploring </li>
<li>Suitable for all skiers, including some challenging black runs</li>
<li>Lots of additional winter activities </li>
<li>Many <a data-udi="umb://document/41babb0d819449c09ee95e90e669265b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/41babb0d819449c09ee95e90e669265b}" title="Ski In Ski Out Holidays">ski-in ski-out</a> accommodation options</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Best apartments, hotels and chalets for February skiing</h2>
<p>Discover the best accommodation options in our February-time skiing resorts across Europe. </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/3d715d1db0644799b7ed5513dac46958" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3d715d1db0644799b7ed5513dac46958}" title="Hotel Kaiserhof"><strong><span>Hotel Kaiserhof 4.5</span>*</strong></a></h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/4005f3bba52b43b997a6530c870938dc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4005f3bba52b43b997a6530c870938dc}" title="Kitzbuhel Alps">Kitzbuhel, Austria</a></h4>
<p><img src="/media/13105147/kaiserhof_winter-338x161.jpg" alt="HotelKaiserhof" data-udi="umb://media/0212936fd5f54610be00f013533f5f26" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="color: #4f4f4f; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Good for: Couples</span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="color: #4f4f4f; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Charming hotel in the perfect ski location, right next to the Hahnenkamm Gondola so you can practically ski-in ski-out. The hotel offers traditional Austrian charm and design with great service and quality dining. There is a lovely wellness area at this hotel, offering a pool, steam room, sauna and more. </span></span></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/a4e20608b1604de3a86296784bdb45af" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4e20608b1604de3a86296784bdb45af}" title="Hotel Magic"><strong><span>Hotel Magic 4</span>*</strong></a></h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/e86e0f4a587e4cd8be3c24d7da459a59" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e86e0f4a587e4cd8be3c24d7da459a59}" title="Pas de la Casa">Pas de la Casa, Andorra</a></h4>
<p><img src="/media/13092300/bergweltref.jpg" alt="hotelbergwelt" data-udi="umb://media/a74fcc4b712e47189c685c50d91bdfbc" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span></span>Good for: Friends / Groups</li>
</ul>
<p>The hotel in centrally located in the resort, next to the slopes and the abundance of cafes, bars and restaurants. It's a popular location due its comfy offerings, well established bar and plentiful buffets so perfect to keep a group of friends busy and entertained out on the slopes all day but also in the hotel for some relaxation. </p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/fa6d932dc383466d847a4b9caacea116" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa6d932dc383466d847a4b9caacea116}" title="Hotel Monte Sella"><strong><span>Hotel Monte Sella 4</span>*</strong></a></h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/0f5433ea301c4a629e7b0da9f972c6e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0f5433ea301c4a629e7b0da9f972c6e5}" title="Chalet Cairn">Plan de Corones, Italy</a></h4>
<p><img src="/media/13062144/italy_dolomites_kronplatz_hotel-monte-sella_exterior.jpg" alt="montesellahotel" data-udi="umb://media/72e9bf4212ab4976af3df91771d1ecd5" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Good for: Families </li>
</ul>
<p>Nothing is too much for these hoteliers, your home is their home in this friendly hotel. The hotel organises free guiding to things like fun-parks and is a close locations to lifts as well as the ski school meeting point, so not far to walk for little legs. The breakfasts and dinners are also hearty and wholesome.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br /><br /></p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/061b256b6bff4767938b3743c3e5e06f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/061b256b6bff4767938b3743c3e5e06f}" title="Hotel Riml">Hotel Riml 4.5*</a></h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/5c5a68def0234451a0e7113b85bac993" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5c5a68def0234451a0e7113b85bac993}" title="Hochgurgl">Hochgurgl, Austria</a></h4>
<p><img src="/media/13080380/riml-exterior-view.jpg" alt="hotelriml" data-udi="umb://media/e567e9fb063346a29997b3787ce99b9e" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Good for: Solo travellers</li>
</ul>
<p>This<a data-udi="umb://document/41babb0d819449c09ee95e90e669265b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/41babb0d819449c09ee95e90e669265b}" title="Ski In Ski Out Holidays"> ski-in ski-out hotel</a>, has a lot to offer including a rooftop spa and an handy on-site shop for supplies. This hotel also doesn't charge for single supplements so is ideal for solo skiers or snowboarders. The accommodation is aimed at adults, so offers accommodation for 14+ ages. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/6c71c21d057d4b469aabb11642450e35" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6c71c21d057d4b469aabb11642450e35}?accommodationNode=23569&amp;programCode=GBINA&amp;tourOpCode=ING&amp;catalogue=010&amp;obArrGateway=ITCH&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;propertyCode=ITCH0107&amp;boardBasis=HB&amp;unitCode=B4&amp;transportType=FLT&amp;departureDate=19/12/2022&amp;duration=7&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;childages=" title="Hotel Alpenrose" data-anchor="?accommodationNode=23569&amp;programCode=GBINA&amp;tourOpCode=ING&amp;catalogue=010&amp;obArrGateway=ITCH&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;propertyCode=ITCH0107&amp;boardBasis=HB&amp;unitCode=B4&amp;transportType=FLT&amp;departureDate=19/12/2022&amp;duration=7&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;childages=">Hotel Alpenrose 3*</a></strong></h3>
<h4><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/1a5883a1530346a9ab78607d76c2e656" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1a5883a1530346a9ab78607d76c2e656}?accommodationNode=23569&amp;programCode=GBINA&amp;tourOpCode=ING&amp;catalogue=010&amp;obArrGateway=ITCH&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;propertyCode=ITCH0107&amp;boardBasis=HB&amp;unitCode=B4&amp;transportType=FLT&amp;departureDate=19/12/2022&amp;duration=7&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;childages=" title="Jungfrau Ski Region" data-anchor="?accommodationNode=23569&amp;programCode=GBINA&amp;tourOpCode=ING&amp;catalogue=010&amp;obArrGateway=ITCH&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;propertyCode=ITCH0107&amp;boardBasis=HB&amp;unitCode=B4&amp;transportType=FLT&amp;departureDate=19/12/2022&amp;duration=7&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;childages=">Jungfrau, Switzerland</a></strong></h4>
<p><img src="/media/13051910/austria_kuhtai_hotel-alpenrose_exterior-winter-night.jpg" alt="hotelalpenrose" data-udi="umb://media/5855c0166d4347fe8df7a3422070d3c2" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Good for: Short ski breaks</li>
</ul>
<p>A modern, alpine style hotel with a traditional, homely feel that provides great service and exceptional cuisine. It has a relaxed feel and is a short walk to the resort centre, so easy to reach if you fancy dinner or a drink in town. The hotel offers a shuttle bus to the lifts so no time is wasted when you are visiting for a short ski or snowboarding trip. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/bc23c629c2294dfb837ab6a087f45bee" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bc23c629c2294dfb837ab6a087f45bee}" title="Chalet Le Cedre Blanc">Chalet Blanc 5*</a></h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88}" title="Meribel">Meribel, France</a></h4>
<p><img src="/media/13080747/fra_mer_lecedreblanc_ext_17.jpg" alt="chaletblanc" data-udi="umb://media/b34c711c8228436d812b41a8f0493ace" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Good for: Après Ski</li>
</ul>
<p>High-quality chalet set over 3 floors equipped with a sunny terrace for piste viewing, open log fire and a sauna. You can make use of the open plan lounge area to enjoy dinner and drinks or the accommodation is not too far from the resort centre where there is plenty of <a data-udi="umb://document/89595b9898014c5fbd93f5619c64b079" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89595b9898014c5fbd93f5619c64b079}" title="Apres Ski Holidays">après ski fun</a> to be had.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2>FAQ's for skiing holidays in February</h2>
<p><strong>Why is it good to ski in February?</strong> - February is a great time to ski, usually the worst of the winter weather has passed so the days are a bit longer and warmer and the weather is a bit more predictable. It is also a good time for families to go as half-term falls in this month. </p>
<p><strong>What are the snow conditions in February?</strong> - February is generally known as a good time for snow as there has been a few months build up of snow fall prior, so the slopes are well covered. It's also early enough in the season that the snow hasn't started to be melt, or be compacted. There is still often gentle snowfalls so fresh snow is still typical to see. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div> </div>
